   <narrative xml:lang="EN">College Scholarship Program ,Ghana West Africa.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">All students deserve a well-rounded education to prepare them for successful careers.  Two final-year high school students will be selected from each of the sixteen regions in Ghana, totaling 32 students, to be awarded a full-ride scholarship. The program is scheduled to start September 2021-2022 academic year. Together we will make an positive impact, as well as to give these needy but brilliant students from the rural areas of Ghana an opportunity  be productive members in their communities.</narrative>
  </description>
